These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: american, australian, german, japanese, malaysian, mexican, polish
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: folk, house, punk, funk, r&b, indie, rock
 1. the american is somewhere to the left of the fan r&b##5
 2. the german is somewhere to the right of the american##5
 3. the polish is on the left or right of the fan folk##3
 4. the fan rock is in an odd position##4
 5. the australian is somewhere to the right of the american##5
 6. the fan rock is on the right of the japanese##1
 7. the australian is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the polish is on the right of the fan folk##1
 9. the fan house is on the far left or far right##3
10. the fan funk is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
11. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the fan rock##5
12. the malaysian is on the left of the mexican##1
13. the mexican is in the middle##1
14. the fan punk is somewhere to the left of the german##5
15. the fan indie is somewhere to the left of the fan r&b##5
16. the fan r&b is not the polish##6
17. the american is on the left or right of the fan indie##3
18. the fan house is not the german##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7      |
| Nationality   | american | japanese | malaysian | mexican | polish | german | australian |
| Pet           | funk   | indie    | rock       | folk     | punk    | r&b   | house |

