 4. the fan house is on the left of the colonial house##1
 5. the colonial house is somewhere to the left of the futuristic house##5
 6. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
 7. the modern house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 8. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the fan classical##3
 9. the fan pop is somewhere to the right of the fan d&b##5
10. the art-deco house is on the right of the fan hip-hop##1
11. the fan hip-hop is not the colonial house##6
12. the fan classical is on the far right##1
13. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan d&b##5
14. the fan house is the palace house##1
15. the art-deco house is on the left of the fan house##1
16. the fan pop is somewhere to the right of the wooden house##5
17. the colonial house is on the right of the fan house##1
18. the fan house is somewhere to the left of the fan d&b##5
19. the fan d&b is on the right of the fan trance##1
20. the fan soul is on the right of the fan hip-hop##1
21. the fan soul is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5

.:: Answer ::.
