 7. the person eating pear is on the left of the accountant##1
 8. the freelancer is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person eating garlic##3
10. the scientist is somewhere to the right of the person eating plum##5
11. the person eating onion is somewhere to the right of the person eating strawberry##5
12. the person eating carrot is on the far right##1
13. the journalist is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
14. the journalist is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
15. the scientist is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the person eating garlic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |     5     |     6      |     7     |
