.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-4::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  dancer, electrician, entrepreneur, musician, photographer, software-developer, teacher
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, november, december, july, march, february, january
 1. the electrician is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 4. the dancer is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1
 6. the photographer is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 7. the entrepreneur is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the software-developer##5
10. the person who's birthday is in january is not the software-developer##6
11. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the electrician##5
12. the dancer is in an even position##4
13. the person who's birthday is in june is not the teacher##6
14. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in june and the entrepreneur##2
15. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
16. the dancer is on the left of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |      3       |    4    |       5       |         6          |      7      |
