 8. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 9. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person eating banana##1
10. the person who's sport is surfing is in the middle##1
11. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
12. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
13. the person who's sport is baseball is not the person eating cauliflower##6
14. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##5
15. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
16. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left or far right##3
17. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person eating nectarine##5
18. the person eating pear is not the person who's sport is water-polo##6
