7 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, swisher, tiparillo, bolivar, dunhill, blend, pall-mall
 1. the dunhill-smoker is on the far left##1
 2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 3. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
 4. the person drinking tea is not the swisher-smoker##6
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
 6. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
 8. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 9. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the dunhill-smoker##5
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
11. the person drinking water is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the swisher-smoker##2
12. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##5
13. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
14. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
15. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the pall-mall-smoker##5
16. the pall-mall-smoker is not the person drinking water##6
17. the person drinking milk is the dannemann-smoker##1
18. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##5

