 8. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
 9. the person eating avocado is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
12. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the person eating garlic##5
13. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
14. the owner of the mouse is the person eating raspberry##1
15. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |   3    |     4     |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Food          | avocado | pumpkin    | cherry | raspberry | garlic  | apricot | spinach |
| Music-Genre   | goldfish  | bird | pony    | mouse     | hamster | horse    | lizard    |

